    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera represents a pinnacle of mechanical preservation, featuring the coveted 3.6L naturally aspirated flat-six engine and a tactile 6-speed manual transaxle. The vehicle boasts a documented IMS bearing retrofit and rear main seal replacement, ensuring long-term powertrain reliability. Chassis dynamics are optimized via the factory M030 sport suspension, providing exceptional lateral stability and communicative steering rack feedback. The exterior retains its showroom-depth luster, while the undercarriage is remarkably clean, free of any oxidation or fluid weepage. Equipped with four-piston monoblock calipers and cross-drilled rotors, the braking system offers immediate, fade-free deceleration. This is a turn-key, collector-quality example for the uncompromising driver.",
